				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you just keep tracking things it will pretty much max out on it's own.  For level 15 your max tracking skill would be 80, though as fast as the lower levels go I would be mildly surprised if yours was capped already.  If it's a concern for you, just hit that track button repeatedly during downtime in a group.  I can tell you that my tracking was at 200 at level 40 without ever having done anything particularly special to raise it.  Foraging on the other hand...<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=879001" target="_blank" class="postlink">Trotter</a> 65 Half-Elf Ranger of Karana [Stromm]</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
