				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">you don't have to track a particular target, no, just keep hitting the track key...or you could macro it like I did.  hit alt + O to bring up Options, click on the keyboard tab, click on select category, scroll down to Macro, then hit any key.  I used the right arrow key so that every time I made a rite turn track automatically came up.  my skill was maxxed and capped pretty early as well.</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
